    "en": {
      "title": "Warrant against Lahiru Weerasekara recalled",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The arrest warrant issued against the national organizer of the 'Youth for Change' movement Lahiru Weerasekara was recalled by Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage on Thursday (25).",
        "A warrant was issued for Weerasekara's arrest for failing to appear for a case, and he appeared in court through counsel.",
        "The warrant was issued as he failed to appear in the case where he was named as being part of an unlawful protest in Fort, Colombo in 2017.",
        "Delayed Super Diesel cargo being unloaded, distribution to continue tonight",
        "Time for Ranil to fulfil pledge on repealing PTA made five years ago \u2013 Sumanthiran",
        "Deputy Police Chief testifies in probe on assault on journalists"
      ],
